description: OPEN HOUSE SAT 3/15, 11AM-12PM.  Welcome to 691 East 8th Street! Unit 1 is a beautiful 2 bedroom 2 full bath brick rowhouse condo in South Boston's desired East Side neighborhood. Gorgeous open concept and living area with central air, nest thermostat, and laundry in unit. This pet-friendly condo is ideally located two blocks from M Street Beach and offers a unique layout with two levels of living space, storage in basement and new private deck. Just a few minutes to shops, restaurants, and all that South Boston has to offer. Easy access to the 7 and 11 bus routes and easy highway access.
